---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 554
  - Title: The Imitation of Christ
    Location: III iv 4
Tags:
  - Life-Love=Grace=Liberty
---
O Lord, how entirely needful is thy grace for me, to begin any good
work, to go on with it, and to accomplish it.

For without that grace I can do nothing, but in thee I can do all
things, when thy grace doth strengthen me.
